To install xmonad and taffybar, first install gobject-introspection by pacman.
Then install xmonad, xmonad-contrib, xmonad-utils, taffybar with stack.

Finally, move build into ~/.xmonad.
=======
First of all, install gobject-introspection by pacman.

To install xmonad, install following packages with stack.
However, install them independently; like
    stack install xmonad
    stack install xmonad-contrib  .etc.:

    xmonad, xmonad-contrib, xmonad-utils, dbus, utf8-string

To install taffybar, run quick-start.sh.
